Check the automation folder for the automations yaml files you can copy paste.


##1 sunscreen
Checks every minute the conditions of sunscreen (if actual conditions met the SET values of the helpers), when al conditions met the helper: sunscreen_conditions_down will be true.
can be used whitout modifications, because all logic is in sunscreen.yaml
This automation, sends a notification to telephone and controls the awkning.
!! replace notification device or methode by your own !!

it include a former separate script: sunscreen_google_sheets
Sends every minute all helpers set values and the actual sensor data to a google sheet to debug.
!! optional!!
